      "recording_attendee_id": "7ff73f2d-dbb3-4bb7-a7a9-2a75ef58de7e",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "Well, Goodness. I apologize. Uh I'm calling uh, to speak in regards to marketing. Sure. Uh, who handle that then now?"
