      "recording_attendee_id": "7ff73f2d-dbb3-4bb7-a7a9-2a75ef58de7e",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "actually where we started student housing at Uw Madison. So I wasn't sure if how things were going with your current marketing? Uh most of the people that I've talked with around this time. Um, are you looking to get out of their current contracts due to um, you know, poor performance or?"
