      "start_time": 78.65,
      "recording_attendee_id": "205347b6-5282-471c-b7fb-523a0552f0a5",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "normally I would agree with you, but it's just a, it's a weird time of year where we're already like locked in, at least at least until like july for most of our contracts. We couldn't make any changes right now. We wanted to just because of our budget,"
